{"tid":1346310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完尋晚元朗單野好灰既 入！！","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T06:01:27.000Z","uid":123138,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d2df3cb19465b8481ad91e1c7752694ecf5697a3","tid":1346310,"uid":123138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"有巴打整合尋晚元朗單野做片 做文宣好 比其他人睇又好<br />\n要記住尋晚元朗同中上環發生既事 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中上環開左36槍 唔可以比佢不了了之</span></span></strong> <br />\n反送中仲未完 依家先真正開始！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z4_o6cM6eNk&amp;feature=youtu.be[/url[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZ4_o6cM6eNk%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%5B%2Furl%5B%2Furl%5D&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIKC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=a578fa3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z4_o6cM6eNk&amp;feature=youtu.be[/url[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n1. 撒回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撒回暴動定義<br />\n3. 撒回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 追究警隊濫權 （尋晚兩單都入依條數）<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n利申： 愛國愛黨 擁護一國兩制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa7a47723637c836b2df3471a223fc377688db8","tid":1346310,"uid":48780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:56:55.000Z","msg":"中英文對照，不斷更新！<br />\n<br />\n中上環元朗都有，歡迎手足比貨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zznkheM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzznkheM.png&h=441a3683&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKRExN8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKRExN8.png&h=2983821c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/toBX3SW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtoBX3SW.png&h=7bbe24aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nw1hjrj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNw1hjrj.png&h=59a6aae4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NyoeZE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NyoeZE.png&h=6a53de67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【文宣】文宣圖集中地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345959</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4d8f3cfcea5f65878b59126448478416c9e127bc","tid":1346310,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"［無政府狀態］元朗恐怖襲擊將成民間自治催産士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1346084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1346084</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"840829bb38bd394d5ef7326eea4aaf2024330c2a","tid":1346310,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"87e49cf474e1d217d8e4d9f3aa8227b62ceb45ca","tid":1346310,"uid":36065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:57:31.000Z","msg":"唔好灰 企出黎"},{"pid":"047dc9cdd9e5801404c95267bf7cb03ce06b8e98","tid":1346310,"uid":12587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:58:53.000Z","msg":"推 唔好灰<br />\n自己香港自己救"},{"pid":"94396011bd38bc2efe89767e00103f90dd6d525f","tid":1346310,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:59:35.000Z","msg":"近千名元朗白衣人在元朗雞地及西鐵站內，手持長傘、竹枝及鐵通，追打身穿黑衣人士。元朗區議員黃偉賢今早在電台節目中表示，他昨日亦在元朗現場，當時，有白衣人向著他的方向，呼喊要打他，他隨即向警方求助，惟警方拒理，並驅車離開。他以「無法無天」來形容白衣人及警方昨晚的行動，並計劃今日到元朗警署抗議。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，昨晚與另一名元朗區議員杜嘉倫在元朗現場，當時有十多部衝鋒車在附近。其後有一部私家車停下來，並跳出幾名白衣人，衝向他並說要打他。他隨即拍打旁邊警車的車門，坐在司機位的警員隨即校低車窗，詢問他發生什麼事。他說︰「我是元朗區議員，這幾位白衣人說想打我，我要求保護。」他指，該名警員聽到後，隨即校回玻璃窗，拒絕受理並開車離開。就有關情況，TOPick正向警方查詢，暫未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n對於有市民指昨晚一直未見警方在現場執法，黃偉賢指，在晚上七時許，已有街坊致電報警表示有大批白衣人在元朗YOHO一帶聚集，但卻被警方CUT線。惟警方卻指稱在晚上十時四十一分才收到報案。他形容︰「警方都無法無天，根本就係放水。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，有市民亦致電電台指，目擊昨晚港鐵元朗站襲擊事件。他表示當時警方看著一批白衣人士離開，但卻沒有採取拘捕行動，只是舉起警棍大聲叫。他指，當時該批白衣人手持棍和藤條，在警員面前行過，而市民則大叫「打人」，但警方向沒有任何執法行動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2407150/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2407150%2F&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIKC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=32f82f62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2407150/</a>"},{"pid":"58b7603d343360e4b6b592086f6fd66ed15dabdd","tid":1346310,"uid":194403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3295d412d9f6604cc7cf3d9b26b98a3e03197c13","tid":1346310,"uid":111955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:00:26.000Z","msg":"唔洗灰，全香港市民都支持覆桌"},{"pid":"f4f6a8d0a9e5e4e6525783e42d5c9de8084f28ed","tid":1346310,"uid":45518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:00:47.000Z","msg":"冇灰, 只有憤怒"},{"pid":"acdc83cf4970d8b8d97b93444bc8f91b62ecb0f9","tid":1346310,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4f6a8d0a9e5e4e6525783e42d5c9de8084f28ed","tid":1346310,"uid":45518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:00:47.000Z","msg":"冇灰, 只有憤怒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:01:06.000Z","msg":"入黎正想打呢句"},{"pid":"3d840941c9df6aa3a6962bb550d138f27a336ed4","tid":1346310,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"87a792d2e43ebb2c403e600aca82c449eba2d210","tid":1346310,"uid":123138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa20eeb49ece346e7d140f99a320f121728b55e2","tid":1346310,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"呢個世界以暴易暴拳頭鬥大好正常，儍豬，唔駛灰既，凡事梗有辦法解決。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3475fd2755c7931196768f9a5429c40f20e8d554","tid":1346310,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198b49ccc8ba58902cc22e8006a5b0aafa1299c4","tid":1346310,"uid":123138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推比更多手足睇"}]}